outputs.output_descr:
An 18 month partnership project to support IIM implement the NIP, with an emphasis on anti-corruption, began in September 2005  key stakeholders include government agencies as well as NGOs.  A UNDP-IIM Capacity Building Project Team was formed to implement the project. 

•NIP implementation action plan developed through participatory workshops
•Staff development programme through ToT / fellowships 
•Information and knowledge dissemination

project_descr: Capacity Development of the Integrity Institute of Malaysia for the Implementation of the National Integrity Plan
